		<td width="600" height="50" colspan="3" align="center" valign="middle" bgcolor="#00aeef" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:22px;line-height:26px;color:#ffffff"><a href="http://ncsthechallenge.org/jobs" style="text-decoration:none;color:#ffffff;font-weight:bold" target="_blank">NATIONAL CITIZEN SERVICE SUMMER 2016</a></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="600" height="25" colspan="3" align="center" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:20px;color:#222222">
			
			<table width="550" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tbody><tr>
			
			<td align="left" valign="top"><a href="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/photos/ncstc_staff-sideimg-skill2_211014.jpg" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/photos/ncstc_staff-sideimg-skill2_211014.jpg" alt="" width="250" height="300" border="0"></a></td>
			
			<td align="left" valign="top"><p><strong>The Challenge is the UK's largest provider of NCS</strong> - an exciting youth and community programme which whisks 15 -17 year olds away on four weeks of adventure, skills building and community volunteering. This year will see over 42,000 young people graduate from NCS. The success of the programme relies on our seasonal staff to support the programme.</p>
			
			<p>This summer we have a massive 4,500 paid roles on offer for people of all skills and experience levels - if you’re looking to develop your own skills and have a huge impact on young people’s lives, these roles are for you.</p></td>
			
			</tr></tbody></table>

		</td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
