		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:18px;line-height:22px;color:#010101"><strong>OUR SEASONAL ROLES</strong></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="center" valign="top"><img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/staffing/Images/ncstc_hr_290914.jpg" width="550" height="22" border="0" style="display:block"></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:20px;color:#222222"><p>
We offer a mix of residential, non-residential or community-based roles ranging from four days to four months in London, Surrey, Bucks & Berks, West Midlands, the North-West or Yorkshire. 
<p><strong>Leader and Management roles</strong>: If you're a natural leader and have experience guiding and managing groups of people, you could be a perfect candidate for our leader roles. Join us on the programme or in our regional offices and hone your management skills in one of our leader roles.</p>

<p><strong>Youth and Mentor roles</strong>: Our mentor roles are perfect for enthusiastic and encouraging individuals who are looking to build on their leadership experience. Take on the Senior Mentor or Senior Community Facilitator role, and watch your group of young people grow throughout the programme.
		
		<p><strong>Practitioner roles</strong>: These specialist practitioner roles are ideal for those who specialise in drama, photography, enterprise, media, or art. If you're dedicated to your craft and want to share your love of it with a group of young people, come and facilitate workshops on our NCS programme.</p>
		
		<p><strong>Inclusion roles</strong>: We're dedicated to ensuring that the NCS programme is accessible to each and every young person. For this reason, we're looking for individuals with significant experience supporting people with additional needs and/or difficult behaviour to work with a young person on a 1-2-1 basis throughout their NCS journey.</p>

<p><strong>Apply now or browse all of our seasonal roles, <a href="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/jobs/#available-opportunities" target="_blank">here!</a></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
