		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:18px;line-height:22px;color:#010101"><strong>THE NCS PROGRAMME</strong></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="center" valign="top"><img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/staffing/Images/ncstc_hr_290914.jpg" width="550" height="22" border="0" style="display:block"></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:20px;color:#222222"><p>The NCS programme is made up of four parts, over 3 or 4 weeks (depending on location):</p>
		
		<p><strong>NCS: Personal Challenge</strong>: A group of between 54-80 young people head off to the great outdoors for a week of adventure, outdoor activities and team building.</p>

<p><strong>NCS: Team Challenge</strong>: The teams return to their local communities and work together to discover a new skill, learning how to use their skill to make a positive impact in their community.</p>

<p><strong>NCS: Real Challenge Design</strong>: Teams identify something they want to change or improve in their local communities and spend the week planning a social action project and campaign.</p>

<p><strong>NCS: Real Challenge Action</strong>: The young people take their social action projects to the streets and campaign for their cause with the general public.


		<p><strong>To find out more about the NCS programme <a href="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/programme/" target="_blank">check out our website!</a></strong></p>

		
		<p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HipmFuhICtQ&feature=youtu.be" target="_blank"><img src="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/assets/New_staff_video_2016.JPG" alt="Click to watch full clip" width="550" height="430" border="0" style="display:block"></a></p></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="600" height="50" colspan="3" align="center" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:18px;line-height:22px;color:#010101"><strong>WHEN DO THE NCS PROGRAMMES RUN?</strong></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="center" valign="top"><img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/staffing/Images/ncstc_hr_290914.jpg" width="550" height="22" border="0" style="display:block"></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:20px;color:#222222">
		
			<table width="550" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tbody><tr>
			
			<td align="left" valign="top"><p>This year we're running the NCS programme throughout the summer holidays, and then again during Autumn half term.</p>
			
				
					<p><strong>Summer Programme:</strong></p>
<p>Late June until late August</p>
			
			<p><strong>Autumn Programme:</strong></p>
<p>October half-term with some weekends in November</p>

<p><strong>Interested? <a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/Login.aspx?signup=1" target="_blank">Sign up here.</a></td>
			
